'''Ndumsa''' (maa ndunsa), keewal mum ko '''dumsi''', ko kuullel ladde.

Tawetee hannde ko he lesdi ɓaleeri. Ko duroowel jemma, woɗɗotaako ndiyam. Nagge mum wa'i ko no nagge wuro nii. Alaa galaaɗi (luwe). Ko ngaari mum ndii waɗi galaaɗi. Ngaari-ndumsa ana wi'ee kadi paparaari-ndumsa. Ana siiwɗa to baŋŋe wutte oo, ana ɓalwa, ana furɗa wano cefe na'i nii. Ko noon ndumsa siforii. Ana jibina kala saanga. Ngaari-ndumsa rewan e nagge mum wano nagge wuro nii, nagge ngee jibinan caggal lebbi jeenay. Ndumsa ana waɗi holsere, ana ñaamee. Wo leɗɗe kecce e huɗo durata. Ɓuri heewde hoɗde ko e farooji.

Ko barooɗe, cewɗi (buutooji), pobbi (bonooji) keewata sonngude ɓikkon kon ñaama kon. Ndumsa so mawnii ana waawi dogude ko yahata wa 63 km e nder waktu gooto. Wo ɗuum waɗi newanaaki kuulle ñaam-teewuuji ɗee nanngude ɗum.
